data.description: BRAND NEW HOME.Fabulous floorplan--with an OVERSIZED 3 CAR GARAGE! This home features a main floor study, extended hardwood flooring, gas fireplace, and large kitchen with island. The Colorado room is spacious enclosed patio perfect for entertaining. The master bathroom features granite counters and custom tile.Front yard landscaping is included.
